4.title: Clip: Wonder Woman Warrior Battle

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds DC - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

4.plot: Take off into an epic Lego D.C. Super Heroes battle against the buildable Ares figure with his horned helmet, giant sword and shield. Use Wonder Woman's superhuman powers and iconic sword and shield to tackle the mythical deity, then team up with pilot Steve Trevor in his fighter plane with flick missiles.

5.title: Clip: Super Hero Girls Bumblebee Helicopter

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds DC - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

5.plot: Watch out. The angry red kryptomites are trying to steal the crystals to make more little monsters. Help bumblebee(TM) shake them from her helicopter before they can get to the storage space at the back. Fire the stud shooters to disarm the angry little creatures and keep the crystals safe.

6.title: Clip: Justice League Knightcrawler Tunnel Attack

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds DC - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

6.plot: Fight for the Mother Box with Batman's Knightcrawler! Drive and crawl with Batman's all-terrain vehicle and reclaim the Mother Box from the evil Parademons, in this exciting LEGO DC Comics Super Heroes Knightcrawler Tunnel Attack set. The Knightcrawler features 4 posable limbs, each with 2-wheel tracks, plus dual 6-stud rapid shooters and an opening cockpit for Batman. Lego 76086.

7.title: Clip: Battle of Atlantis

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds DC - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

7.plot: Protect the precious Mother Box from the evil Parademon. Team up with Aquaman and the Atlantean guards to stop the super-jumping Parademon stealing the Mother Box in this all-action LEGO DC Comics Super Heroes Battle of Atlantis set. The underwater Atlantis scene features a grand arch to knock over with the Parademon's Super Jumper. Lego 76085.

8.title: Clip: Flying Fox: Batmobile Airlift

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds DC - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

8.plot: Unleash the Batmobile from The Flying Fox. Team up with the Justice League against Steppenwolf and the Parademons to claim the precious Mother Box, in this exciting LEGO DC Comics Super Heroes Flying Fox: Batmobile Airlift Attack set. The Flying Fox features a 2-minifigure cockpit with a lift-off canopy, 2 spring-loaded shooters, and 2 stud shooters. Lego 76087.

imdb.plot outline: Lego DC Universe Super Heroes lets your child play, invent and create with a colorful world of superheroes. With these play sets your child can build famous scenes and enjoy the role play between all the heroes and villains. Every option brings fun and lots of learning. Themes include Batman, Superman, Justice League, Green Lantern, The Flash, Aquaman and others.
